[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering constructors and methods**\n\nI'm thinking about constructors and whether their names should be classified as \"methods,\" like using <init>? I'm also contemplating reachability metadata and how sometimes constructors might function as methods. It seems beneficial to check examples to clarify these concepts further. I wonder how other programming languages might handle this, too, since naming conventions can vary. There’s a lot to explore in this area!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_09a2af978a4013a50169f7c95e472c819d9d80c948f76c484b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp98lgTqn227TdCfntnLbVMMurrtDxT6IEhtrqZMD3wNBqPuc6oepX_L5v6k8XSLFOE0xz3IHcFz-vR3PkW9vmYvb1D3LMVa-YxBHWB9jU99TSG43dKTIF6a54Xsm-z3TKcf_dIC1mRf7vTsgOhauM87q4S1BU-2AomcsD6NVyeyCFaKkI2UHp8N17EubvPlH4hYqoc-bgJk3QBONY4PyXrKPLPjcXtAQyjdNwc_xkaVD01-yTpG54wG26lZwAYnLSyq4TJezmL-0tJmK6Ltc-pvXPsrQz2nkYREVzAzb041ky_7b5znfuiOSzMXOq9PmTuIusWEW1djF9t7cxmEsfR3TRKPIHp6j1860PTMws4kg8-C5xfzCoeVnPYjUay6LKsCmvAPZZCQ8OHZ2UUsBhe28H2D8pAkQdATmZKa7OPSLBJ2QAaBIVmdPLs8UvubTtNibT3jafFWPsseppoosPaH_KAIgVp6BC6d7u2wn_lRTxA2anvtN0FsmRXkCWGbWwF7kxxjn9QPRIuwwUxo6upFTY0I0HcDB7y2kOUDrI4RqqPtv5aVoGBTF5sCKJM3I0prPyESl5ZIZ2IwqxTU7i5CbE5ndCZzVVpo_mFDDCOr00pe3TjTB6LH0hV663Zmr0-ytXQR2GeYSZ7nxeHZsr_7yJs_Za3SKqi5q9Z3meeMZ40rr5Z19ZP2vxMr8s3NPkBj7-EaibSUW8tVS1wIbztNwjDGF6lwfwbO86obC7oxseJYDtKR58NeK-S5AH8z8oUBqQXobi2iBjSPybQJYjJY0p_IQ3Tt2Ikomwn9V6C20G1ssLapuS5yu2UKGAbAJpt4P7qhv46NeTxyf5Io3IfHcYz3RryMY7X_f504g3esfYNDtTT0aT5-NDXTWWJV6kRON3ugX5bRKo6lgWfjPgy0CEMUvsBGqmhjBQ-xyp5rYtp1bM3ULgn_msyl8Hn7x1J8RylOLYPK0_-NOosJnyuhqKwYYRvaPnupprvgT4q68wjXiGckTUh6SSdtcnA0h8V0kSsDI1fdWZZV7SehdLwnnG9XZcOl14DHxmaW1iZT21-yS2RzY0AWYZk61YvwNim_vDvAS6jEzp9p8UHXMgOSRKCZqdxyo-JyNGPnrxV0FUTbQ=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering constructors and methods**\\n\\nI'm thinking about constructors and wheth